author: CBR
description:
What are the biggest questions we have going into Season 5 Volume 2 of Stranger Things?

CBR's Caralynn Matassa and Katie Doll delve into the fan theories that made us question if everything we think we know about the upcoming finale is a lie.

From Eleven and Will Byers true parentage to the true source of Vecna's powers. Is Nancy Wheeler the final girl we all think she is? Will Steve Harrington make it to the end? All this and more, you can find right here.
